Nothing needs to be added to .gitignore since only a source code file (`.jsx`) was added and there are no build artifacts, dependencies, or temporary files in the changes.
```
# Build artifacts
dist/
build/
*.o
*.obj
*.out

# Dependencies
node_modules/
venv/
.venv/
__pycache__/
.mypy_cache/
.pytest_cache/

# Editors
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*.tmp

# Logs
*.log

# Environment
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Coverage
coverage/
htmlcov/
.coverage

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
```
